# Funnel Skill Registry

- Every time a skill is created, revised, or published, update `src/funnels/_skill-drafts/SKILL-MAP.md`.
- Required fields to add or update: codice, nome Cursor, cartella definitiva, file draft, stato.
- When a skill moves from draft to published: update stato from `draft` to `published` in SKILL-MAP.md.
- Skill `name` in frontmatter must always match the Nome Cursor in SKILL-MAP.md exactly.
- When publishing a skill, replace all internal code references (A1, A2, B1, etc.) with the corresponding Nome Cursor from SKILL-MAP.md.
